    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Units equal to one meter in a straight line; used to measure the amount of shelf space occupied by archival materials within a specific collection, as well as piping, wiring, and other things that are linear in orientation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
